2011-09-26

A puppet recipe to install Sonar

Usage

class { "sonar" :
}

- or -

class { "sonar" :
  version => "2.10",
  user => "sonar",
  group => "sonar",
  service => "sonar",
  home => "/usr/local",
  download_url => "http://dist.sonar.codehaus.org/sonar-$version.zip"
}
